SIMPLE: unadvised
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unadvised
<hw>Un`ad*vised"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
prudent; not discreet; ill advised.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Done without due consideration; wanton; rash;
inconsiderate; <as>as, an <ex>unadvised</ex> proceeding</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Un`ad*vis"ed*ly</wf> <pr>(#)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos>
-- <wf>Un`ad*vis"ed*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unaffected</ent>⟦br⟧
